Title: A Path of Dejavu Journey
DateModified: '2019-02-21'
DatePublished: '2019-02-21'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/a-path-of-dejavu-journey
SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: dewi puspitasari
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: 'This will be a dejavu journey, from a desire in the childhood that has been
  brought into an everlasting dream to experience in my life. I know no more about
  Portugal but hearing the name from my mother, my teachers and found its name in
  the History book when I was in childhood: Portuegese as the explorers who reached
  the Islands where Indonesian has grown various tremendous spices.  The Portuguese
  forts lays in some sea shores of Indonesian archipelagos have proven that the expansion
  of the country existed before. the bricks or stone of the wall, the color of the
  building, the contour and the shape, the huge walls with canon, will they be the
  same as what other colonized countries have as the replica of their common building
  in Portugal?'
